{"tid":2219914,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"關於會員TV8231(#245847) 於遊戲台洗版自推一事","createTime":"2020-09-27T08:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T18:17:21.000Z","uid":43750,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"413c61d7e32e792d8ad9a28763f051bbedeed261","tid":2219914,"uid":43750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:30:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">會員TV8231(#245847) </span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/245847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/245847</a><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n個撚屌日日都起遊戲台瘋狂自推佢果2個垃圾POST</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Discord打機約戰平台招人，宜家已經有1,200人喇，玩乜GAME都無任歡迎！</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2218508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2218508</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［彩虹冒險＋時空亂鬥］私服「２０２０年」最新資訊</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2216648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2216648</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">如果佢2個POST係有正常討論遊戲都算<br />\n但撳入去睇發現咁多頁都係得佢自己一個自推<br />\n翻查返過往紀錄會發現, 呢條撚屌起遊戲台已經維持左呢個行為<ins>起碼一年<br />\n</ins><br />\n而且佢大部分post都同 彩虹冒險私服 呢個遊戲有關<br />\n不禁令人懷疑該會員是否為該遊戲私服團隊既打手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗱 我唔係鳩嗡, 係有跡可尋<br />\n該會員曾經就畫質問題開左下面呢個POST查詢 (美瑞希=TV8231)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>擺片上Youtube之後畫質變差問題</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631817</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuYt9f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwuYt9f3.png&h=5fae2e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">撳入去佢提供既Link會發現個Youtube Channel就係遊戲私服既Channel</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GibGKs8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGibGKs8.png&h=47778435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">該私服既Facebook專頁 </span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6473do0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6473do0.png&h=b3d57fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/spnewgame/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fspnewgame%2F&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=9fea3bcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/spnewgame/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">話佢同唔係私服背後既團隊or打手真係無人信 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n分分鐘係大陸仔開檔賺你班傻仔錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVp1KMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVp1KMr.png&h=99f0266f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知每日有幾多傻仔課金俾佢賺呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvoaC6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbvoaC6s.png&h=9e647d12&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">另外上面佢自推果2個post會發現佢係誘導人入去佢個Discord Group</span></strong><br />\n佢標榜希望人數上到5000人, 懷疑係想借Discord群組達5000人後利用群組獲利<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyWLrUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyWLrUu.png&h=266708b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">結論係個撚屌根本就係借連登搵食 <br />\n兩個POST都唔係正常討論POST, 沾污遊戲台<br />\n<br />\n希望Admin正視問題</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"61830f5f40ebb813821315aff23986c06763a5b7","tid":2219914,"uid":43750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"推到Admin收佢皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}